Text: ABN Amro Futures Execution AgreementShari Stack told to me to get in contact with you about the things she was working on for me before she jumped ship I work for Gary Hickersons group in Australia and Shari was looking at a futures execution agreement with ABN Amro in Australia and I was wondering if you have seen it Also Westpac have told me that the ISDA with them has been finally agreed is this correct Regards Shane
Deals with CitibankCan you tell me whether ENA has an ISDA with Citibank and what entity it is with I am contemplating doing an interest rate swap with them Regards Shane

FW Access AgreementsSara We are setting up access to JP Morgans online FX system These are the documents they sent us to get signed before they will give us access Are you the correct person to send them to Regards Shane Original Message From mailto Sent September To Dallmann Shane Subject Access Agreements Forwarded by Claire BurleyCHASE on Tracey Tommasini Legal Department Fax Number To cc Claire HASE Anna Bell HASE Subject Access Agreements At the request of Claire Burley attached please find the Access Agreement ChaseFX Electronic Trading Service Additional Terms Covering FX Transactions Authorized Users Single FX Trade NetMatch Schedule NetMatch Authorized Users between Enron North America and The Chase Manhattan Bank Please note that the attached documents can be viewed and printed but not edited Please print review and complete the Address for Notices which is located on page five of the Access Agreement as well as the Designation of Authorized Users Forms and have an authorized officer of your organization sign each of the agreements and return two hard copy executed agreements to the attention of Tracey Tommasini Legal Department The Chase Manhattan Bank London Wall London ECY AJ United Kingdom for further execution Please provide an incumbency certificate signed by the Corporate Secretary for the person or persons who sign the agreements and form Should you have any questions please contact Andrew Hamper on Tracey Tommasini Assistant See attached file Access Agreement US lawdoc See attached file Chase FX Electronic Trading Servicedoc See attached file Additional FX Termsdoc See attached file Authorized UsersSingle FX Tradedoc See attached file NetMatch Schedule with Settlement Instructionsdoc See attached file NetMatch Authorized Users with Settlement Instructionsdoc
